We have all bloody read it,

45
00:02:09,060 --> 00:02:10,337
我说得还不清楚吗?
do I make myself clear?

46
00:02:10,337 --> 00:02:12,073
再清楚不过了 大臣
Abundantly, Minister.

47
00:02:12,591 --> 00:02:14,426
很抱歉 坐
I'm sorry. Sit down.

48
