Humphrey, we have got to slim down the Civil Service.

49
00:02:20,862 --> 00:02:22,840
我们部门里有多少人?
Howmany people have we got in this department?

50
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:25,930
这个部门吗? 哦 我们部很小的
This department? Oh, we're very small.

51
00:02:25,930 --> 00:02:27,298
小? 有多小?
Small? How small?

52
00:02:28,061 --> 00:02:31,291
-不知道...  -2千人?
- I don't know... - 2,000?

53
00:02:31,802 --> 00:02:32,975
3千?
3,000?

54
00:02:34,244 --> 00:02:36,444
我想 大概2万3千人吧 大臣
about 23,000 I think, Minister.

55
00:02:36,444 --> 00:02:38,806
2万3千人?
23,000?

56
00:02:39,092 --> 00:02:41,099
在行政部?
In the Department of Administrative Affairs?

57
00:02:41,099 --> 00:02:44,435
这2万3千人都在管理其他行政人员?
23,000 people just administering other administrators?

58
00:02:44,767 --> 00:02:47,532
我们得研究一下体制和工作方法 看看哪些是冗员
We'll have to do a study to see who we can get rid of.

59
00:02:47,532 --> 00:02:49,848
-去年我们倒是研究过 大臣阁下  -结果呢?
- We did one of those last year, minister. - And?

60
00:02:49,848 --> 00:02:52,276
结果表明我们还需要再增加五百人
It transpired we needed another 500 people.

61
